{
  "uid": "bada-overview",
  "title": "BADA Overview",
  "tags": ["bada", "overview"],
  "timezone": "Asia/Seoul",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "env",
        "label": "환경",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
        "query": "label_values(http_requests_total, env)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {"selected": true, "text": ["All"], "value": ["$__all"]},
        "sort": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "title": "BADA Overview (dev + prod)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "상단 **환경(`$env`)** 셀렉터로 dev/prod를 함께(All) 또는 개별로 볼 수 있습니다. 시계열은 `by (env)`로 환경별 분리됩니다.\n\n- HTTP/분석 지표는 dev·prod backend 모두 Prometheus 스크랩(env 라벨)으로 표시됩니다(prod는 `prod_monitoring_enabled` 필요).\n- **Worker 메시지 처리량**은 prod worker가 크로스-VPC로 Prometheus 미수집이라 **dev만** 표시됩니다. prod worker는 `BADA Prod Worker`(CloudWatch)에서 관측하세요."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "총 요청수 (5분)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (env)(rate(http_requests_total{env=~\"$env\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{env}}"}]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "에러율 (5xx)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 3},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (env)(rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\",env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) / sum by (env)(rate(http_requests_total{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) * 100", "legendFormat": "{{env}}"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "percent"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "P95 응답시간",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 3},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) by (le, env))", "legendFormat": "{{env}}"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "분석 실행 (성공/실패)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 3},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "sum by (env)(bada_analysis_runs_total{status=\"success\",env=~\"$env\"})", "legendFormat": "성공 {{env}}"},
        {"expr": "sum by (env)(bada_analysis_runs_total{status=\"failed\",env=~\"$env\"})", "legendFormat": "실패 {{env}}"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "요청수 추이 (method·env별)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 7},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{env=~\"$env\"}[1m])) by (method, env)", "legendFormat": "{{env}} {{method}}"}]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "응답시간 (P50/P95/P99, env별)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 7},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) by (le, env))", "legendFormat": "P50 {{env}}"},
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) by (le, env))", "legendFormat": "P95 {{env}}"},
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) by (le, env))", "legendFormat": "P99 {{env}}"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Worker 메시지 처리량 (dev only)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 15},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(worker_sqs_messages_total{env=~\"$env\"}[5m])) by (task_type, env)", "legendFormat": "{{env}} {{task_type}}"}]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "상태코드 분포 (env별)",
      "type": "piechart",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 15},
      "datasource": {"uid": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (status, env)(http_requests_total{env=~\"$env\"})", "legendFormat": "{{env}} {{status}}"}]
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 3
}
